口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"63c2276ae0d71a0d3eed52fa0c1554cef26803df","tid":332702,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:35:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾多年先夠？ <br />\n咁係唔係九成以上美國人都唔可以講本土 佢地先著陸三百年"},{"pid":"ec7a734eb98cf7f6df1ae48cbc4eee11bfcb7acf","tid":332702,"uid":20625,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:47:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾多年先夠？ <br />\n咁係唔係九成以上美國人都唔可以講本土 佢地先著陸三百年</blockquote><br />\n美國人接納不嬲多元文化結合社會<br />\n只要對社會有貢獻，邊個都係美國人<br />\n佢地好少會特別區分本土（印第安人）與否<br />\n亂尻咁引用例子無助討論嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f1f9724e0eee8bd6cc1f15a8c0bc9f37a44b3b8","tid":332702,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:52:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾多年先夠？ <br />\n咁係唔係九成以上美國人都唔可以講本土 佢地先著陸三百年</blockquote><br />\n美國根本冇本土意識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且佢地政策為左補償印第安人而有好多優待同特權，而連登仔就想同原居民平權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f14c95e63c94f70316033999459bc19f82c1bf5","tid":332702,"uid":3659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>民族主義唔係講血統。</blockquote><br />\n因為講血統你即刻變做大陸仔<br />\n所以你咪唔講血統囉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講血統嘅話，南方人同中原人/圖博/維吾爾/蒙古/滿人血統都差好遠，根本冇咩「中國人」血統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以梁啟超先格硬拉曬所有清帝國境內民族，聲稱都係所謂「中華民族」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講血統我地根本唔係咩中國血統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為根本冇依樣野"},{"pid":"cd5dc9ddaa6540c532ecb4aeaab4ba2b47ab6559","tid":332702,"uid":81197,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就純種5p"},{"pid":"1a458f3db4f3a311a1a31a905d9ccd32f5ae0bd7","tid":332702,"uid":32765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:58:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你就純種5p</blockquote><br />\nn賓都5p <br />\n你老母就5p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0802e04e68c326ea7bff22857a2eab4c21e12f71","tid":332702,"uid":3659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-24T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本土唔係咩邊個原居係一個地方最耐先有權去講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扭曲曬本土定義再打稻草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"854cacb7c1fcf83f7af96c2f55bdbd3e3d7c4b06","tid":332702,"uid":32765,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T00:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本土唔係咩邊個原居係一個地方最耐先有權去講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扭曲曬本土定義再打稻草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地移民去香港教當地人咩係香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e988d4cebfc6d116306cc9244ac9b72cc89fdcc","tid":332702,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T00:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾多年先夠？ <br />\n咁係唔係九成以上美國人都唔可以講本土 佢地先著陸三百年</blockquote><br />\n美國人接納不嬲多元文化結合社會<br />\n只要對社會有貢獻，邊個都係美國人<br />\n佢地好少會特別區分本土（印第安人）與否<br />\n亂尻咁引用例子無助討論嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁本土派係想好似美國咁 有個移民制度 有貢獻先收 唔係阿豬阿狗都收"},{"pid":"c7ce234c1d2f3abedacc1b80d8c8331362e017c6","tid":332702,"uid":3659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T00:14:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>班近100年先偷渡入黎既支那移民學人講本土，真係笑撚大人個口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全部都係支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本土唔係咩邊個原居係一個地方最耐先有權去講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n扭曲曬本土定義再打稻草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地移民去香港教當地人咩係香港人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港開埠以來，就係移民城市，人口多數都係由外來移民構成，但係依班移民同後代係依個地方構建左本土意識，去維護依個地方文化同價值觀，有咩問題？<br />\n<br />\n佢地唔符合「香港人」定義咩？如果只有原居香港先叫香港人，咁香港境內一定冇香港人，因為清帝國試過遷界，要南方沿海居民向內遷移，香港再無原居民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9bf149e75