他人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n新移民透過拉高自己同移民一樣<br />\n移民透過拉低原居民同自己一樣<br />\n做法唔同 但原本既人既利益係冇佐<br />\n不過你地仲要冇得益 即係多鳩餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1efac5e3d48bddd5476e871f991e1791151c2231","tid":332702,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實全人類祖先都係非洲人, 支持牛屎仔去非洲要求分返撻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係都非牛屎啦弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家邊D人話冇地呀"},{"pid":"cd2e0c4167d5d22bc6d40aeb6ccc1d3565963d40","tid":332702,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"驚死你唔撚明<br />\n你鬥死晒班牛屎佬<br />\n你都唔會有任何著數<br />\n換既係一班比你更仆街既鬥地主前輩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fca474b5e9ff1a1d8d7d5fbb81a226dfac5af650","tid":332702,"uid":81075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實全人類祖先都係非洲人, 支持牛屎仔去非洲要求分返撻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係都非牛屎啦弱智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家邊D人話冇地呀</blockquote><br />\n九唔柒搭八...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n牛屎仔話自己祖先係到住所以有地, 咁牛屎仔祖先都係非洲住過, 你地去埋非洲拎撻地咪岩囉<br />\n<br />\n另外, 大部份香港人都係話收返丁權, 無話要分撻地<br />\n<br />\n個個丁權post都見到你條柒頭皮係到發表d缺乏邏輯嘅言論, 你慢慢繼續9up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有得笑下都好"},{"pid":"5d4563ff64c2cde66003cdf9f6fae308b5371f21","tid":332702,"uid":91931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T10:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實全人類祖先都係非洲人, 支持牛屎仔去非洲要求分返撻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係都非牛屎啦弱智<i